Package at.ac.univie.se2.ws21.team0404.app.utils

Interface IChangingData<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - data type to be wrapped
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChangingData, ChangingDataOnMainThread, ChangingDataWithViewState, ViewState
    public interface IChangingData<T>
    Wraps data in an observable container. Observers implementing IChangingData.Observer will be notified in case the data changes. Notifications will also be sent on initial registration of an observer.

    Do not forget to unobserve(Observer) to prevent memory leaks. Tip: For convenience the ChangingDataWithViewState decorator can be used to automatically remove observers on view destruction and also pause notifications for invisible views.
